    "description": "DSV India Consulting Pvt Ltd invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Pune location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout DSV India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nDSV India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DSV India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
